## 3. `column` command may not exist

```bash
brew list --formula | column
```

👉 Problem:

* `column` is not guaranteed installed

### ✅ Fix

```bash
if command -v column &>/dev/null; then
  brew list --formula | column
else
  brew list --formula
fi
```

