## 9. No logging (big miss for production)

Add:

```bash
LOG_FILE="$HOME/Vantix_setup.log"
exec > >(tee -a "$LOG_FILE") 2>&1
```

👉 This turns your script into:

* Debuggable
* Auditable
* Professional

